    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/f9942fd327d4af149dd66a99178153ad.poster.avif?t=1732283999\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/f9942fd327d4af149dd66a99178153ad.webm?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/f9942fd327d4af149dd66a99178153ad.mp4?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎来到 Farm Renovator DEMO，在这里您将翻新、扩建并经营一个美国农场。选择自由、任务多样、以创造性的方式经营业务和处理困难情况是这款游戏的关键要素。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >演示版包括 </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >翻新第一栋建筑</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >修缮鸡舍</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 种工具</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >客户服务</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在店里卖鸡蛋</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >割草</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >砍树</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >演示的主要功能：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/313b8e599d3827ef503f46d8a5a21fd9.poster.avif?t=1732283999\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/313b8e599d3827ef503f46d8a5a21fd9.webm?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/313b8e599d3827ef503f46d8a5a21fd9.mp4?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更新</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 买下一个废弃的农场，将其恢复昔日的光彩。清除杂草和垃圾，修复设施的墙壁，按照自己的喜好进行粉刷和装饰。修复设备，购买无法修复的设备，邀请客户，这样你就有资金进行扩张、进一步翻新和改进。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/949a7793762cdec35bac5009f0755642.poster.avif?t=1732283999\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/949a7793762cdec35bac5009f0755642.webm?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/949a7793762cdec35bac5009f0755642.mp4?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扩张 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >做好管理、投资和扩张，为越来越多的客户提供服务。您可以扩大产品范围。在演示版中，您有机会更新您的商店，这将使您在开始时赚取一些现金。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/9efe18837487404a20770789d3e5af68.poster.avif?t=1732283999\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/9efe18837487404a20770789d3e5af68.webm?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3241900/extras/9efe18837487404a20770789d3e5af68.mp4?t=1732283999\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >运营 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一旦农场开始生产，客户服务将成为您成功的关键。明智地管理您的时间和优先事项，扩大您的产品范围。注意产品种类和质量。您将获得发展资金。</p>",
